It took 30 min for us to receive our food.
(there was only one other table for 2 seated) When she brought our food out to us she placed it in front of us and immediately turned and walked off.
She did not ask if everything looked ok or if she could bring us anything else.
I actually  did need sauce and cheese for my italian sausage sandwich and my friend needed ranch for her fries.
