If you live within 3 miles of this place.....it's your local "Grille".
It is a place to go after work or an after "workout" place to get  drink.
Jen the bartender, is awesome.
It's like walking into your local Starbucks and she already is making your drink.
Yes, this place is in a shopping mall pad, so the atmosphere is all locals...but I think that's why we all come here.
The staff knows who comes on Mondays, Tues. Weds.....that's us!!!!
etc.
Due to the fact, we only come here after our workouts.....we have only had their veggie pizza...not bad.
But, Jen makes a great a low calorie concoction...which  I can't name right now-working on the patent.
You come here because the bar service is great and they have cold beer!

